    "created_at": "2016-05-24T18:05:45Z",
    "updated_at": "2016-05-24T19:20:37Z",
    "body": "I believe @paulcbetts means, for example, `preload.js`:\n\n``` js\n'use strict';\nrequire('dependency-with-side-effects');\nconst otherDep = require('other-dep');\nconst main = require('preload-main');\notherDep.config({ foo: 'bar' });\nmain.init(otherDep);\n```\n\ninstead of `main.js`:\n\n``` js\n// ...\n{\n    // ...\n    preload: [\n        'dependency-with-side-effects.js',\n        'other-dep.js',\n        'configure-other-dep.js',\n        'preload-main.js'\n    ]\n    // ...\n}\n// ...\n```\n"
  },
